'''Christ Ravynel Inao Oulaï''' (born 6 April 2006) is an Ivorian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Trabzonspor]] and the [[Ivory Coast national football team|Ivory Coast national team]].

==Club career==
Inao joined the youth academy of [[JMG Academy]] at the age of 12, where he finished his development.<ref name="auto"/> On 6 July 2024, he joined the French [[Ligue 2]] club [[SC Bastia|Bastia]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.spiritu-turchinu.com/actualite/breves/3027-bastia-recrute-christ-ravynel-inao-oulai|title=Le SC Bastia recrute Christ Ravynel Inao Oulaï|date=6 July 2024|website=Spiritu Turchinu}}</ref> He made his senior debut with Bastia in a 4–0 [[Coupe de France]] win over FC Freymingon 16 November 2024.<ref name="auto"/> On 14 April 2025, he scored his first career goal in a 5–2 victory over [[Stade Lavallois|Laval]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/707046/stade-laval-bastia |title=Bastia 5–2 Stade Laval |publisher=ESPN |date=14 April 2025 }}</ref>

On 22 August 2025, he transferred to the Turkish [[Süper Lig]] club [[Trabzonspor]] on a 5-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/article/christ-inao-oula-signs-trabzonspor-102600114.html|title=Christ Inao Oulaï signs with Trabzonspor from SC Bastia|first=Foot Africa·1 min|last=read|date=22 August 2025|website=Yahoo Sports}}</ref> Later that year, on 25 October, he scored his first goal for the club in a 2–0 win over [[Eyüpspor]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/750007/eyupspor-trabzonspor |title=Trabzonspor 2–0 Eyupspor |publisher=ESPN |date=25 October 2025 }}</ref>

==International career==
Inao was called up to the [[Ivory Coast national football team|Ivory Coast national team]] for a set of friendlies in November 2025.<ref>{{cite web |title=Côte d'Ivoire : un nouveau et un retour surprise dans la liste des Eléphants pour jouer la qualif'|url=https://www.afrik-foot.com/cote-divoire-la-liste-pleine-de-surprises-demerse-fae-pour-les-retrouvailles-avec-herve-renard |website=afrik-foot.com |date=1 October 2025}}</ref>

